      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "只要一个公式，就能把整个家族写清楚。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "translate",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "translate-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/translate-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "把 x 换成 x 减 h，图象就整体向右平移 h 个单位。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "translate",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "translate-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/translate-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "在末尾加上 k，图象就整体向上平移 k 个单位。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "translate",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "translate-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/translate-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "h 管左右，k 管上下，平移不改变曲线的形状。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "scale",
      "line_id": "scl-1",
      "filename": "scale-scl-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/scale-scl-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "乘上系数 a，图象在竖直方向被拉伸或压扁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "scale",
      "line_id": "scl-2",
      "filename": "scale-scl-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/scale-scl-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "在 x 前面乘 b，图象在水平方向被压缩或拉宽。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "scale",
      "line_id": "scl-3",
      "filename": "scale-scl-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/scale-scl-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "a 越大越瘦高，b 越大左右越紧凑。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "flip",
      "line_id": "flp-1",
      "filename": "flip-flp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/flip-flp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "当 a 取负，整条曲线沿 x 轴翻个身，上下颠倒。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "flip",
      "line_id": "flp-2",
      "filename": "flip-flp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/function-transform/xiaoxiao/flip-flp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "当 b 取负，曲线沿 y 轴镜像，左右对调。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "function-transform",
      "section_id": "interaction",
